title: Dream Unchained - Kate Douglas
description:
Mac's team of telepaths has proven more powerful than he'd
imagined, but time grows short, Zianne's life force is fading and an
entire race of Nyrian slaves is at risk--as well as the future of life
on Earth.

As the final minutes speed by much too quickly, a last ditch effort is
made to save the world, to save a dying race, and to save a
love that transcends time.



Dream Unchained (Dream Catchers #2)
By Kate Douglas
Language: EN
Pages: PDF 783 - EPUB 502
